Not reported previously for the dataset was the measurement of weight. Animals were weighed individually immediately prior to initiation of testing and morphine treatment using a pan balance accurate to 0.01g. Animals were again weighed after completion of the chronic morphine administration paradigm. To calculate % weight change, the following formula was used:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
